  "detailed_description": "Neon Little Soul is a frenetic and fun action platformer game, a little gem of minimalist pixel art, retro style and arcade spirit.<br>Your most loved one was kidnapped. Now you come to the rescue. Climb the dangerous floors of the neon building to reach your quest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/81102003a33140a9f8ab5a4d5562c860.poster.avif?t=1707315429\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/81102003a33140a9f8ab5a4d5562c860.webm?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/81102003a33140a9f8ab5a4d5562c860.mp4?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>TRAPS</strong><br>Spikes, explosive tiles, electrical devices, moving walls, acid drops and many other traps await the brave.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/4dc1f1506d15a3b5ba87eab347f16b87.poster.avif?t=1707315429\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/4dc1f1506d15a3b5ba87eab347f16b87.webm?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/4dc1f1506d15a3b5ba87eab347f16b87.mp4?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>ENEMIES</strong><br>They move by land and air. They attack with their fists, their poisoned tongues, their fireballs, and their hard heads. They do not rest. They are coming for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/634166ec66f1fb2850803dfd2a2a9bae.poster.avif?t=1707315429\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/634166ec66f1fb2850803dfd2a2a9bae.webm?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/634166ec66f1fb2850803dfd2a2a9bae.mp4?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>POWER-UPS</strong><br>Get amazing power-ups to boost your skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/d3af2a6e763d0d516d6a4e4247a7a485.poster.avif?t=1707315429\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/d3af2a6e763d0d516d6a4e4247a7a485.webm?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/d3af2a6e763d0d516d6a4e4247a7a485.mp4?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br>Fun!<br>Frenetic!<br>Minimalist pixel art, retro style and arcade spirit!<br>Countless levels!<br>Many enemies!<br>Many more traps!<br>And incredible power-ups for you!",
  "about_the_game": "Neon Little Soul is a frenetic and fun action platformer game, a little gem of minimalist pixel art, retro style and arcade spirit.<br>Your most loved one was kidnapped. Now you come to the rescue. Climb the dangerous floors of the neon building to reach your quest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/81102003a33140a9f8ab5a4d5562c860.poster.avif?t=1707315429\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/81102003a33140a9f8ab5a4d5562c860.webm?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/81102003a33140a9f8ab5a4d5562c860.mp4?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>TRAPS</strong><br>Spikes, explosive tiles, electrical devices, moving walls, acid drops and many other traps await the brave.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/4dc1f1506d15a3b5ba87eab347f16b87.poster.avif?t=1707315429\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/4dc1f1506d15a3b5ba87eab347f16b87.webm?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/4dc1f1506d15a3b5ba87eab347f16b87.mp4?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>ENEMIES</strong><br>They move by land and air. They attack with their fists, their poisoned tongues, their fireballs, and their hard heads. They do not rest. They are coming for you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/634166ec66f1fb2850803dfd2a2a9bae.poster.avif?t=1707315429\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/634166ec66f1fb2850803dfd2a2a9bae.webm?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/634166ec66f1fb2850803dfd2a2a9bae.mp4?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>POWER-UPS</strong><br>Get amazing power-ups to boost your skills.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/d3af2a6e763d0d516d6a4e4247a7a485.poster.avif?t=1707315429\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/d3af2a6e763d0d516d6a4e4247a7a485.webm?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2479510/extras/d3af2a6e763d0d516d6a4e4247a7a485.mp4?t=1707315429\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>FEATURES</strong><br>Fun!<br>Frenetic!<br>Minimalist pixel art, retro style and arcade spirit!<br>Countless levels!<br>Many enemies!<br>Many more traps!<br>And incredible power-ups for you!",
